5: So, um, did you have fun?
8:
But of course! I mean, this is

9:

How's the training for your new

61:

68:

someone I knew. You look very
mature for your age...
70:

72:
I'm sorry, that was a strange thing to

75: Sorry, Alk... I need to take care of this.
78:
Okay. I've got more shopping to do

83:
Miss, would you like to talk about it?
It might help you feel better.
89:
So, this man you loved, he passed

92:
Yes. He succumbed to it shortly after

94:
My parents are trying to find me

96:
He's not a bad man... No, in fact, he's

99:

103:
But my parents... They said if I don't

105:
Goodness, I apologize for

108:
The worth of your life is something
only you can decide.
111:
I know it hurts when people don't
accept you... Or when someone you
care for isn't there anymore.
114:
But that doesn't make you worth
any less.
119:
You get to choose what you want to
do, and what's important to you.
122:
Even if that person isn't who you
wanted the most, if you choose to
care for them, and love them...
124:
Then maybe one day you can be
happy. That's what I think, at least.
127:
Thank you. I feel a little better after

129:
Then I suppose it was worth going

134:
Oh, sorry. I guess you don't use that

137:
This is something only you can
decide, but...

Even after you get married, I'd like to

148:
Yes. I... feel like I got a lot off of my

151: Wait... Now that I think about it...
157:
Who the hell are you to decide what

169:
Huh? Luca, what's wrong? Are you

197:

203:
